+
+## Risk Assessment
+
+| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
+|------|-----------|--------|-----------|
+| Token replay attack via captured pairing token | Medium | High | Genesis plan 003 / 006 |
+| Regression in error handling with no tests | High | Medium | Genesis plan 004 |
